<template>
	<AgreementLayout :leftText="$t('buttons.go_back')" @onClickLeft="onClickLeft">
		<AppIframe :url="url" />
	</AgreementLayout>
</template>
<script setup>
import AgreementLayout from '@/components/layouts/AgreementLayout.vue';
import AppIframe from '@/components/main/AppIframe.vue';
import { computed } from 'vue';
import { useRouter } from 'vue-router';
import { useStore } from 'vuex';

const store = useStore();
const router = useRouter();

const url = process.env.VUE_APP_OFERTA;

const entry = computed(() => store.state.Auth.entry);

function onClickLeft() {
	return entry.value === 1
		? router.push({ name: 'TermsOfUseView' })
		: router.push({ name: 'SettingsView' });
}
</script>
